==English==
===Proper noun===
'''Garinagu'''

# An [[ethnic]] people in the [[Caribbean]] area, descended from a mix of [[Amerindian]] and [[African]] people, with many in Central America and the United States. 

====Usage note====
While '''Garinagu''' is the (plural or collective) term for the people, the term Garífuna refers to the individual and the language.

====Synonyms====
*[[Black Carib]]s
*[[Garífuna]]
*[[Garifune]]

